<item>
            <title>[LUCENE-2088] AttributeSource.addAttribute should only accept interfaces, the missing test leads to problems with Token.TOKEN_ATTRIBUTE_FACTORY</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/LUCENE-2088</link>
                <project id="12310110" key="LUCENE">Lucene - Core</project>
                        <description>&lt;p&gt;This is a blocker, because you can call addAttribute(Token.class) without getting an error message.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I will commit the fix and restart the vote for 3.0. This also applies to 2.9, but there is no Token Attribute Factory. But I will merge to 2.9, too, if a 2.9.2 comes.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
